# \dontrun{
   setMetadataStandard("19115-3")

   md <- ISOSampleDimension$new()
   md$setSequenceIdentifier(ISOMemberName$new(aName = "name", attributeType = "type"))
   md$setDescriptor("descriptor")

#> [1] TRUE
   gml$setQuantityTypeReference("someref")

   md$setUnits(gml)
   md$setScaleFactor(1)
   md$setOffset(4)
   xml <- md$encode()
